name: Sergeant Major Enfield
Lore: 'Commander of a platoon of Death Star troopers. Maintains security around the detention block area. Often serves as Lt. Shann Childsen''s attache.',
Text: 'When in a battle with another Death Star trooper, adds one battle destiny. Your Death Star troopers are deploy -1 to same Death Star site. Trooper Charge targeting at same or related site is a Used Interrupt. Power -1 when not on Death Star.',
